{"title":"街道诗钞","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"街道诗钞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了服务组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愁人手少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千家如一家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难如山倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗街上喜事多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都唱协作歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你帮我助成风尚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点滴力量汇成河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街巷里弄红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进声中改新貌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍设万能服务站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民生活组织好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个补钉一颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针针线线情意深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗净补好穿身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产不忘缝补人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公共食堂托儿所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大跃进来解放我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家务劳动社会化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安安心心搞工作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔原载重庆日报〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王太婆，笑呵呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见人就把喜事说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子围着锅台转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今我也有工作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天我在托儿所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引着小伢唱山歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上灯下忙学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作手中托。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学了著作干劲高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越搞工作越快活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人和我开玩笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说我和青年差不多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的日子怎么不快活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦里我也笑呵呵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔原载长江日报〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从有了服务站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们孤老得照看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卧病在床两月多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送茶送水又送饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天来几遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问长又问短。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是过去旧社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷苦孤老有谁管。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了党的好领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤老不孤得温暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢党和毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病好决心努力干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔原载湖北日报〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}